 ork is allowed during the fellowship\, full-time is not). Twelve-month fel
 lows produce four articles\, six-month fellows two. Decisions by end of 20
 26. Distinct from FIJ's regular reporting grants. No application fee.\n\nO
 rganisation: Fund for Investigative Journalism (Alicia Patterson Foundatio
 n program)\nLocation: Remote\; fellows may live anywhere\, but projects mu
